metadata.description:
Each Subtle Spirits release is conceptualized with a commissioned piece of label art designed to pair specifically with the spirit inside. 

Gabe Weis is a renowned mixed-media artist living in the Bay Area and uses a stream of consciousness approach to his work.

Subtle Spirits is teaming up with Gabe Weis to bring you one of the most unique and rare whiskies the world has ever seen. 

What you will get with the NFT purchase: 
- 1 NFT 
- 1 Bottle of Subtle Spirits Prodigal Son, numbered and signed by Gabe Weis
